Cleric Rework
	- Access to Elemental Spells

Earth
	- Pact:
OK		- must actively oppose defilers (unlike druids who are defensive)
OK		- must teach the cycle of life
OK		- must teach agriculture
	- Granted Powers
		- 5th: ignore earth 1/day, 1 round/level
		- 7th: gate element 0.3 m³/(level - 6), always stone
OK		- eliminate tracks (only on earth, not snow or mud)
OK		- encasement (caixão pra dormir dentro da terra)
OK		- meld into stone 1/day
		- +2 vs earth spells
OK		- halve defile area with Wisdom check
Air
	- Pact:
OK		- must actively oppose slavery
OK		- must oppose unfair imprisonment
OK		- must protect earth and water (for future hurricanes)
	- Granted Powers
OK		- 5th: ignore air 1/day, 1 round/level
OK		- 7th: gate element windstorm in a 300m cone
		- breathable air 1/day
OK		- reduce penalty for heat
		- +1 for missile ranged attacks
OK		- +1 CA against missile ranged attacks
OK		- control winds 1/day
		- +2 vs air spells
OK		- feather fall 1/day
Fire
	- Pact:
OK		- must encourage growth of cities, forests and fields
OK		- must defeat the sorcerer-kings and all defilers
	- Granted Powers
		- 5th: ignore heat 1/day, 1 round/level
		- 7th: gate element 0.3m³/(level - 6), 1 round without fuel
OK		- create small flames the size of a match stick
		- affect normal fires 1/day
OK		- cleansing flame (heal, bath, food, restore) 1/day
		- control flames smaller than torch
		- +2 vs fire spells
Water
	- Pact:
OK		- must give water and aid to any in need, except defilers
OK		- must protect and preserve remaining water
OK		- must teach irrigation and cleansing of water supplies
	- Granted Powers
		- 5th: ignore water 1/day, 1 round/level
		- 7th: gate element 0.3m³/(level - 6), no damage, drinkable
OK		- 1/3 daily water from mud/plant/rock
		- 1 water stabilizing skin, heals 1d2 hp
		- +2 vs water spells, -2 vs fire/sun spells
		- +4 vs poison
		- 1 revival skin, heals unconsciousness to 1hp

Silt
	- Pact:
OK		- must advance the silt
		- destroy trees, grasses and fauna that retain moisture
	- Granted Powers
OK		- 5th: ignore silt 1/day, 1 round/level
		- 7th: gate element 0.3m³/(level -6)
OK		- 9th: walk on silt
OK		- 11th: control 0.3m³/level of silt

Sun
	- Pact:
		- must eliminate all gases that filter the sun
		- must remove any obstructions (flatten the planet)
	- Granted Powers
		- 3rd: 1/2 water usage, no ill effects of remaining in the sun
		- 4th: +2 vs sun spells
		- 5th: ignore daylight/sunray spells 1/day, 1 round/level
		- 7th: gate element sunray 4d8 1 square/level

Magma
	- Pact:
		- must grow magma's domain
		- keep magma heated
		- remove nearby water reserves
	- Granted Powers
		- 1st: +2 vs fire/magma spells
		- 5th: ignore magma 1/day, 1 round/level
		- 7th: gate element 0.3m³/level
		- 8th: evaporate 45l of water/level 1/day

Rain
	- Pact:
OK		- protect forests and water reserves
OK		- plant new forests
	- Granted Powers
OK		- 3rd: immune to weather effects; -2 save in the sun; +2 vs water/rain
		- 5th: ignore rain/mud
		- 7th: gate element 0.3m² of rain
OK		- 8th: call lightning 1/day